headline.main: Wood Double Lifts Leeds to 3-1 Win at Birmingham
headline.print_headline: Wood Double Lifts Leeds to 3-1 Win at Birmingham

lead_paragraph: Actual delays in delivering medical care to military veterans remain far worse at Veterans Affairs facilities in North Carolina and Virginia than internal records showed, according to a new report by government inspectors.
